com.communote.server.core.util

Class InitalFiltersVO

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.core.util.InitalFiltersVO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class InitalFiltersVO
extends Object
implements Serializable
    The inital filters value object keeps the filter data of a permalink including the necessary information to be used to initalize the widgets. The VO will be JSONed so be careful with associations.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
